    <link rel="icon" sizes="144x144" href="https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/original/1X/ebb284b1e209aa93c9744227e1374130f8190aec.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/original/1X/477ac7ed14175dfd2deb65ee3c3d83d18a8906b8.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.bootcss.com/font-awesome/4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/style.css">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Orbitron' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="content">
        <nav id="bar">
            <div>
                <a class="nav-link blue" href="https://emacs-china.org/"><i class="fa fa-group" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;Forum</a>
                <a class="nav-link yellow" href="http://book.emacs-china.org" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-book" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;Book</a>
                <a class="nav-link violet" href="http://elpa.emacs-china.org"><i class="fa fa-server" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;ELPA</a>
                <a class="nav-link orange" href="http://donate.emacs-china.org">
                    <i class="fa fa-heart" aria-hidden="true"></i> &nbsp;Donate
                </a>
                <a class="fork-us" href="https://github.com/emacs-china" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i>
&nbsp;Fork Us</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="heading">
            <h1 class="heading-main">
                <span class="img">
<img class="emacs-china-logo" src="./imgs/logo.png"/>
</span>
                <span class="text">Emacs China 捐赠页面</span>
            </h1>
        </div>

        <p>
            各位 Emacs 道友，
        </p>

        <p>
            大家好。
        </p>

        <p>
            为了让 Emacs China 更加健康可持续地发展，从今日起 Emacs China 开始接受社区的捐赠。捐赠的钱主要用于支付域名费用和服务器费用。
        </p>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline1" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline1">关于捐赠说明</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline1">
                <p>
                    如果域名到期，或者服务器到期，会优先使用捐赠余额。 如果余额不足，默认由我(zilongshanren)继续捐赠。直至下一个周期有新的捐赠款为止。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline2" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline2">捐赠的总金额</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline2">
                <p>
                    <%= total_amount.round(2) %> 元
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline3" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline3">捐赠款余额</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline3">
                <p>
                    <%= ( total_amount + total_expense ).round(2) %> 元
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline6" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline6">捐赠方法</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline6">
            </div>
            <div id="outline-container-orgheadline4" class="outline-3">
                <h3 id="orgheadline4">方法一</h3>
                <div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgheadline4">
                    <p>
                        添加 zilongshanren 微信号转帐（注明来意），或者直接通过支付宝帐号 guanghui8827@126.com 转帐（请注明转帐意图）
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="outline-container-orgheadline5" class="outline-3">
                <h3 id="orgheadline5">方法二</h3>
                <div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgheadline5">
                    <p>
                        扫描下面二维码进行捐赠，捐赠金额不限
                    </p>

                    <div class="row clearfix">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <img src="./imgs/weixin-donate.jpeg" class="img-responsive" />
                            <p class="text-center"><strong>微信</strong></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <img src="./imgs/zhifubao-donate.jpeg" class="img-responsive" />
                            <p class="text-center"><strong>支付宝</strong></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline7" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline7">捐赠者列表</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline7">
                <p>
                    (这里没有你的名字？点击<a href="https://github.com/emacs-china/donate/issues/2">此处添加</a> 或者发邮件至 guanghui8827@gmail.com)
                </p>

                <table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


                    <colgroup>
                        <col class="org-left" />

                        <col class="org-left" />

                        <col class="org-right" />
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-right">捐赠日期</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-left">捐赠者</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-left">捐赠金额</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <%= list_donation  %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline8" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline8">捐赠金额用途</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline8">
                <table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


                    <colgroup>
                        <col class="org-right" />
                        <col class="org-left" />
                        <col class="org-right" />
                        <col class="org-left" />
                        <col class="org-left" />
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-right">日期</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-right">授权</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-right">费用（元）</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-left">支出项目</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="org-left">备注</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <%= list_expense %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="outline-container-orgheadline9" class="outline-2">
            <h2 id="orgheadline9">致谢</h2>
            <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline9">
                <p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/li-xinyang">@li-xinyang</a> 改进 <a href="http://donate.emacs-china.org/">http://donate.emacs-china.org/</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</html>
